  <brief_title>Sitagliptin Metformin Add-on Study in Patients With Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multicenter, Double-Blind, Randomized Study to Evaluate the Safety and Efficacy of the Addition of Sitagliptin to Patients With Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus Who Have Inadequate Glycemic Control on Metformin Therapy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
