  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A clinical study to determine the safety and efficacy of sitagliptin in patients with Type 2
      Diabetes Mellitus who have inadequate glycemic (blood sugar) control on metformin therapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
